Module org.im4r0ve
Package org.im4r0ve

Class Anthill

java.lang.Object
org.im4r0ve.Anthill
public class Anthill
extends java.lang.Object
Anthill maintains all the ants that belong to one anthill. It is also maintaining the pheromone map.
